name: ExceptionBacklog
description: A data set containing exceptions that need to be resolved

attributeDefs.name: notes
attributeDefs.description: Notes on usage, purpose and type of exception backlog.

attributeDefs.name: steward
attributeDefs.description: Unique identifier of the person or team responsible for this exception backlog.

attributeDefs.name: process
attributeDefs.description: Unique identifier of the automated process that processes this exception backlog.
